    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a dependable option for anyone needing a solid daily driver. Mechanically, the engine and transmission are functional, though you might notice some typical wear-and-tear sounds and a slightly aged suspension. The exterior has several visible scuffs, some minor paint oxidation on the roof, and a few small dings consistent with its age. Inside, the cabin is clean but shows wear on the driver's seat and some fading on the dashboard plastics. It\u2019s a reliable car that gets the job done, provided you don't mind these cosmetic and minor mechanical signs of use.",
