    {
      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Check out this dependable ride that's ready for its next chapter! While it shows some honest wear and tear from its years of faithful service, it remains a solid, functional vehicle that's perfect for someone looking for reliable transportation at a great value. With a little bit of care, this car still has plenty of miles left to offer and represents a fantastic opportunity for a budget-conscious buyer!",
