    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good condition and has been well-maintained, offering a reliable driving experience for its next owner. The engine runs smoothly and the transmission shifts as it should, with no major mechanical issues to report. While there may be some minor cosmetic wear consistent with its age, the interior is clean and all essential features are fully functional. It\u2019s a solid, dependable car that is ready for the road.",
